{"tid":1637800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協就禁蒙面法投訴向政府發律師信 要求李家超即日回覆","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:17:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aadf87aa6609d63bc325a88f9daea78d997a5edd","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"政府10月5日起實施《禁止蒙面規例》，保安局局長李家超曾承諾記者的採訪工作仍會受保障，但記協過去幾天已接獲多宗有關警員執法時，強行扯脫記者防毒面罩的投訴，本會對此強烈不滿。<br />\n<br />\n記協今早已透過律師去信政府，要求李家超確認記者可繼續合法採訪公眾活動及佩戴面罩，同時確認前線警員已收到清晰指令，不可要求正在採訪的記者除去面罩。鑑於事態緊急，為免造成更多誤解、衝突甚至濫捕，本會要求李家超在今日辦公時間內回覆，並保留法律追究權力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVPxVjR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVPxVjR.jpg&h=4da719b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2zVQGZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2zVQGZR.jpg&h=79c2f0e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8976421ce2851bd509bafe5d9630dc926b6c0445","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/posts/10157392985470309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKJA.official%2Fposts%2F10157392985470309&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnImrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=6324b75e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKJA.official/posts/10157392985470309</a>"},{"pid":"558f5aabbc86563565a42cfaafec8c91db97e4cc","tid":1637800,"uid":55162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"記協加油！"},{"pid":"0a6e3f2dabc2cfa5768cd541b675b053ed24a0dc","tid":1637800,"uid":270863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"絕對正確！非常支持！"},{"pid":"731a47a8ab8451ec9c92804251110f8ddcfaf302","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/