e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf53f5701a42dd8a30890e5ea0a0c1d2b3162ce","tid":1637800,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"a541cefb827579e9337085ee41455fd8ad13b979","tid":1637800,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bab7d347c601bd374dcb0320275941c09469090","tid":1637800,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"覆左未呀"},{"pid":"0cc6be9578d67c4631f41440dcdb032cad73d6f6","tid":1637800,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f011c527b1284cd8bbd69834acadd68295e8e8ec","tid":1637800,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd8d45ee9c5ca1f733fe1b1ce4efd97995f43fb","tid":1637800,"uid":278313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"「電光石火之間分辨唔到記者」<br />\n「有暴徒混入假扮記者」<br />\n「已通知前線警員」（但照做）<br />\n「警員壓力大要體諒」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:06:07.000Z","msg":"第3同第4如果相悖<br />\n咁已經無紀律可言<br />\n唔駛處分呀你老母"},{"pid":"80c8f9cfa5d2f3208d0c30f09762e05de4b10f60","tid":1637800,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78748a51c2078c2234985547813aa4138a15cc3c","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c9bd654d5c5bfb0a20f537a24ccb07de49e6dd","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bab7d347c601bd374dcb0320275941c09469090","tid":1637800,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"覆左未呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"好似未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e95db5c85201f9d7248bf921791c7b47bc797c3","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"記協新聞稿：<br />\n<br />\n記協接獲警員扯脫記者面罩投訴 去信政府促保障合法採訪<br />\n<br />\n政府10月5日起實施《禁止蒙面規例》，保安局局長李家超曾承諾記者的採訪工作仍會受保障，但記協過去幾天已接獲多宗有關警員執法時，強行扯脫記者防毒面罩的投訴。記協今早已透過律師去信政府，要求李家超作出三項確認，以保障採訪工作不受新例之影響。<br />\n<br />\n這份致律政司司長鄭若驊、保安局局長李家超及警務處處長盧偉聰的信件，要求確認三點，包括：<br />\n1. 記者採訪公眾活動不會被警方視作參與該活動；<br />\n2. 記者佩戴面罩採訪這些活動並無觸犯禁蒙面法；<br />\n3. 前線警員已收到清晰指令，不可要求正進行合法採訪的記者除去面罩；若警員堅持要求記者除去面罩，該警員亦同樣要除下面罩及出示委任證，讓對方可辨識其身份。而警員核實記者身份後，記者即可戴回面罩。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於事態緊急，為免造成更多誤解、衝突甚至濫捕，本會要求李家超在今日辦公時間內回覆，並保留法律追究權力。<br />\n<br />\n本會重申，各區近日持續出現嚴重及廣泛的暴力衝突，警方更頻繁使用催淚彈及胡椒噴劑，新聞工作者在採訪時，必須佩戴防毒面罩，以免被釋出的有害和刺激物所傷及影響工作。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會<br />\n2019年10月8日"},{"pid":"fdc510ac2bb6e6527b791870a8be0f69714b6bc2","tid":1637800,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"#Kill#<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129e8c034938853a8ce100dfbd1574fdccd16317","tid":1637800,"uid":107414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd8d45ee9c5ca1f733fe1b1ce4efd97995f43fb","tid":1637800,"uid":278313,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"「電光石火之間分辨唔到記者」<br />\n「有暴徒混入假扮記者」<br />\n「已通知前線警員」（但照做）<br />\n「警員壓力大要體諒」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以去狗隊發言人"},{"pid":"8f71f72ac0803bee080fbfdc3da2cc7531686195","tid":1637800,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}